messages.speech: This type of policy covers all the risks covered under Motor Liability policy plus loss or damage caused to the vehicle due to: Accident, Fire, Explosion, Self ignition, Lightning, Burglary, House Breaking, Theft, Riots & Strikes, Earthquakes, Flood, Typhoon, Hurricane, Storm, Cyclones, Malicious Acts, Terrorism, Transit by rail/road, air and waterways and also include towing charges.
